OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMan barred from Ryanair    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fflight over wheelchair     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fweight row                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A man says he was blocked from taking a
OL,6, flight as his wheelchair was too heavy.
OL,8,FBrandon Aughton, from West Bridgford in
OL,9,FNottinghamshire, had been due to travel
OL,10,Fwith Ryanair from East Midlands Airport
OL,11,Fto Malaga on 11 October.               
OL,13,FThe 24-year-old said he was told he    
OL,14,Fcould not board the plane as staff were
OL,15,Funable to lift his specialist chair,   
OL,16,Fwhich weighs about 217kg (417lb), from 
OL,17,Fthe conveyor belt and the hold.        
OL,19,FSwissport, Ryanair's baggage handler,  
OL,20,Fsaid it was "saddened" by the incident.
